00:26:42.790 --> 00:26:43.490
I...

00:26:48.590 --> 00:26:49.330
Biyun.

00:26:49.790 --> 00:26:51.530
I've been tailing Hashimoto these days,

00:26:51.880 --> 00:26:53.660
looking for a chance
to copy the codebook.

00:26:53.880 --> 00:26:55.460
But Gu Yangshan and Luo Han

00:26:55.480 --> 00:26:56.860
acted before I could.

00:26:56.880 --> 00:26:59.090
They killed Hashimoto
and copied the codebook.

00:26:59.590 --> 00:27:01.140
If I didn't act then, I'd lose my shot.

00:27:01.480 --> 00:27:03.490
So I took the risk to snatch it.

00:27:03.510 --> 00:27:04.730
But I failed.

00:27:05.310 --> 00:27:06.620
And right in front of Luo Han,

00:27:06.640 --> 00:27:08.010
I exposed who I really am.

00:27:10.750 --> 00:27:12.420
We now know Gu Yangshan's true identity.

00:27:13.000 --> 00:27:14.290
Luo Han won't make any rash moves.

00:27:19.680 --> 00:27:21.420
But we didn't get the codebook.

00:27:22.680 --> 00:27:24.010
If we try to snatch it from them again,

00:27:25.790 --> 00:27:26.660
it'll be much harder.

00:27:28.160 --> 00:27:30.490
Things are worse than we thought.

00:27:31.030 --> 00:27:33.420
Gu Yangshan already alerted the enemy.

00:27:33.640 --> 00:27:34.900
I secretly took a photo of Hashimoto

00:27:34.920 --> 00:27:35.860
and sent it to the Organization.

00:27:35.880 --> 00:27:38.660
They confirmed Hashimoto is an alias.

00:27:39.000 --> 00:27:41.220
His real name is Sasaki Taro.

00:27:41.240 --> 00:27:42.330
He's Sasaki's...

00:27:42.790 --> 00:27:43.620
son.

00:28:04.160 --> 00:28:06.250
What about the relief worker
who brought him?

00:28:06.550 --> 00:28:07.420
Did you find him?

00:28:08.070 --> 00:28:09.700
We've already checked.

00:28:09.720 --> 00:28:12.220
That relief worker was an imposter.

00:28:12.240 --> 00:28:14.250
And he's disappeared.

00:28:14.920 --> 00:28:16.220
Disappeared?

