00:30:04.680 --> 00:30:05.730
That's like throwing your life away.

00:30:05.750 --> 00:30:08.050
Seriously, that's pure suicide.

00:30:31.680 --> 00:30:33.220
Did anyone see your face?

00:30:35.240 --> 00:30:36.660
Hashimoto Taro was Sasaki's son.

00:30:36.680 --> 00:30:38.490
They'll never let this go.

00:30:38.510 --> 00:30:39.700
The city's about to go on lockdown.

00:30:39.720 --> 00:30:41.700
Grab your camera and get out now.

00:30:41.720 --> 00:30:43.010
