00:31:17.750 --> 00:31:18.860
But I haven't gone there

00:31:18.880 --> 00:31:19.770
for a long time.

00:31:20.480 --> 00:31:22.980
If Sasaki traces it to Yuyin Pavilion,

00:31:23.000 --> 00:31:24.700
he'll definitely suspect you.

00:31:25.920 --> 00:31:27.180
So you have to leave.

00:31:29.640 --> 00:31:30.770
But I think

00:31:32.510 --> 00:31:34.090
you're the one in greater danger now.

00:31:37.000 --> 00:31:37.700
Wu's identity

00:31:37.720 --> 00:31:39.660
has already been exposed to Luo Han.

00:31:39.680 --> 00:31:41.460
If Luo Han gets caught,

00:31:42.480 --> 00:31:43.570
selling out your identity

00:31:44.510 --> 00:31:46.700
could be his bargaining chip
for survival.

00:31:47.790 --> 00:31:48.810
Of course,

00:31:48.830 --> 00:31:50.810
if Luo Han makes it back to Chongqing,

00:31:50.830 --> 00:31:52.730
he'll definitely go to my superiors

00:31:52.750 --> 00:31:54.050
and report who you really are.

00:31:55.550 --> 00:31:57.090
So even if I don't lay a hand on you,

00:31:58.350 --> 00:32:00.620
my superiors will still go after you.

00:32:02.720 --> 00:32:03.380
That's why, Ding Yi,

00:32:04.030 --> 00:32:04.980
