I'm the very sword
in the Sword Thrust Operation.

00:32:15.750 --> 00:32:19.180
As long as I'm here, the mission stands.

00:32:20.510 --> 00:32:21.700
So leaving is not an option for me.

00:32:23.270 --> 00:32:24.620
So this is just you wanting me gone.

00:32:26.030 --> 00:32:27.090
Once I'm out of the way,

00:32:28.750 --> 00:32:30.250
